<plot>The first of a series of six two-reel "Musical Parade" shorts produced in Technicolor for the Paramount 1943-44 production season. The series would continue into 1948, and then were reissued in the early 50's. In addition to listed cast, dancers Adriana &amp; Charly were on hand, as were The Rogers Dancers. Songs included "All the Way" and "At the Mardi Gras."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?357576</url></doc>
